paragraphs.text:
# DATA COMES FROM MANY TYPES AND FORMS!

***Data usually could be in one or more of these categories, depending on the context:***

* *Relational and Tabular Data*
* *Graph and Linked Data*
* *Temporal Data*
* *Text Data*
* *Image and Video Data*
* *Sound Data*
* *Stream Data*

paragraphs.text:
# DATA COMES FROM MANY DIFFERENT SOURCES!

***Data is available from many sources, for example:***

* ***Social Platforms***: *Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, Instagram, etc*
* ***Scientific Data***: *Data Generated or Gathered in Scientific Expriements*
* ***Transactional Data***: *Financial Transaction Data*
* ***Logs***: *System Logs*
* ***Internet***: *Web Traffic*
* ***Web Data***: *Data Imbedded in Web Pages*
